snippet: Fox News correspondent Dominic Di-Natale, whose international reporting took him from Osama bin Laden’s compound in Pakistan to covering protests in Ferguson, Missouri, has been found dead in Colorado, officials said on Friday....

headline.print_headline: Former Fox News Reporter Dominic Di-Natale Found Dead in Colorado
headline.main: Former Fox News Reporter Dominic Di-Natale Found Dead in Colorado

lead_paragraph: Fox News correspondent Dominic Di-Natale, whose international reporting took him from Osama bin Laden’s compound in Pakistan to covering protests in Ferguson, Missouri, has been found dead in Colorado, officials said on Friday.
